  "title": " docs(guide): Add \"Use your own backend\"",
  "body": "This PR adds the guide for using a custom backend with InstantSearch.js: [**Use your own backend**](https://deploy-preview-2943--algolia-instantsearch.netlify.com/v2/guides/custom-backend.html).\r\n\r\nIt will get replicated for all flavors. The only part that will change is the code snippet in \"Using the search client with InstantSearch\".\r\n\r\n~Note that I named the file `proxy-backend.md`, which is going to be the URL to the guide. Let me know if you think of a better name.~\r\n\r\nBefore merging it'll be great to find somewhere to host the Search Client Specification as I refer to it.",
